<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_423" id="211r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_423_r1l13"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Abbte cʒü VValtſachſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_423_r1l14"><expan>Erwirdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l15">Steimpachs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſeinen brief in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſloſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l16">das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vvol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu habt Jr vns vor <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeinen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l17"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf das als Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frewnd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l18">vnd ſie mit ew geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">nem </del> <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> nemlıch vmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l19">einen frid vncʒ auf Pfingſten / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">hab </del> wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l20"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> verſtanden vnd ew in <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> maſʒe darauf <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l21">vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd das <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> gemaint / . vnd vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l22"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch den frıde ſeit her <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd wöllen auch den noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l23">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan></del> biʒ auf pfingſten nehſtkumend 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan></del> <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l24">vnd mainen auch / daʒ Jn <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Steimpach auch <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l25">vnd auch fürbas <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſülle / . 
<add><ab facs="#facs_423_r1l31">des wir vns an ewr <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gencʒlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gelaſſen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch noch <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> vnd das mügt Jr Jm auch alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l26">wol <expan>ſage<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>embıet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / So wöllen wir auch in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit cʒü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l27"><expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> weıden ſchıcken / Alſo / daʒ Jr vnd den cʒeitlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l28">vor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> / vnd wenn Jr vns ſecʒet / würd <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ew vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l29"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Jn ıht dar an <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daʒ man das an <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> auch cʒeıtlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_423_r1l30">davor cʒe wiſſen tü / vnd vvo etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Oculȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_423" id="211r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, abbte czü Waltsachsen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> ,<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Steimpachs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und seinen brief in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beslosze<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>; nu habt ir uns vor
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> seinen <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, auf das als ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vormals mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sie mit ew geredt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
                        nemlich umb einen frid uncz auf <app><note><q type="date">pfingsten</q>22.05.1412</note></app>; und wir
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> verstanden und ew in
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> masze darauf
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und das
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> gemaint. Und wir
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch den fride seither
                                <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und wöllen auch den noch biz auf
                        pfingsten nehstkumend <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> und mainen auch, daz in
                                <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Steimpach auch
                                <expan>gehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch fürbas <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sülle, <add>des wir uns an ewr <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>genczlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gelassen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch noch
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, und das mügt ir im auch also
                        wol <expan>sage<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>embiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; so
                        wöllen wir auch in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit czü
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Weiden schicken, also daz ir und den czeitlich vor
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> und, wenn ir uns seczet, würd
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ew, uns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> in
                        iht dar an <expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz man das an
                                <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> auch czeitlich davor cze wissen tü.
                        Und wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> oculi.</ab>
</div>
